<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="setvbuf" id="setvbuf">setvbuf</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">setvbuf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">FILE</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>stream, <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>buffer, <span class="kw4">int</span> mode, <span class="kw4">size_t</span> size <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

函数setvbuf()为文件流stream设置缓冲区buffer，设置缓冲区大小为size。模式mode可以是：
</p>

<p>
* _IOFBF, 指示使用全缓冲
* _IOLBF, 意味着行缓冲
* _IONBF, 意味着没有缓冲
</p>

<p>

相关主题： <a href="setbuf" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:setbuf">setbuf</a>
</p>

</div>
